        description = "Bypass patterns for evasion of exitProcess calls"
        cape_options = "bp0=$pattern0+0,action0=skip,bp1=$pattern1+0,action1=skip,bp2=$pattern2+0,action2=skip,count=0"

    strings:
        $pattern0 = { 85 C0 0F 88 E8 CE 00 00 8B 45 5A 33 CD 00 00 01 10 } // Skip initial setup
        $pattern1 = { E8 CE 00 00 8B 45 5A 33 CD 00 00 01 10 } // Skip exit address load
        $pattern2 = { 8B EC 00 C9 00 00 00 00 55 00 01 EB } // Avoid conditional jump after call
    condition:
        any of them
}
